NOTICE — third-party and referenced material

- "Lonesome Dove" is a novel by Larry McMurtry (Simon & Schuster, 1985).
  This is an unofficial fan work. The dataset describes the novel's events in
  original prose; the handful of brief quotations are short excerpts used for
  commentary and identification. No book text is reproduced at length.
- River and border geometry derived from Natural Earth (public domain) and
  US Census state outlines (public domain).
- Typefaces (Rye; IM Fell English, English SC, and DW Pica) are licensed under
  the SIL Open Font License and redistributed in fonts/ under its terms.
